OL,3,CDismembered remains of two men found
OL,4,Cwith axe in woods, murder trial told
OL,6,FTwo men whose dismembered remains were
OL,7,Ffound in woodland in Sticker in
OL,8,FCornwall met their alleged killer at a
OL,9,Fresidence for homeless people in
OL,10,FNewquay, a court has been told.
OL,12,FThe trial of 40-year-old James
OL,13,FDesborough began today, Wednesday 24
OL,14,FJune. He has pleaded not guilty to the
OL,15,Fmurders of 57-year-old Claudio
OL,16,FAquilino, and 43-year-old Daniel
OL,17,FColeman.
OL,19,FHe has previously pleaded guilty to
OL,20,Fpreventing the lawful burial of the
OL,21,Ftwo men's bodies, the jury was told.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
