OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782400703
OL,3,CDismembered remains of two men found
OL,4,Cwith axe in woods, murder trial told
OL,6,FThe court heard that Desborough and
OL,7,Fthe two men had been living at the
OL,8,FSandy Lodge Hotel in Newquay and that
OL,9,FDesborough had left the hotel three
OL,10,Fdays before Claudio Aquilino was last
OL,11,Fseen alive.
OL,13,FDesborough is accused of murdering
OL,14,FClaudio Aquilino sometime between 17
OL,15,FApril and 7 July 2025, and Daniel
OL,16,FColeman sometime between 2 June and 7
OL,17,FJuly 2025.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
