OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782400703
OL,3,CDismembered remains of two men found
OL,4,Cwith axe in woods, murder trial told
OL,6,FA large police search took place in
OL,7,FSticker in July 2025, with specialist
OL,8,Fforensic officers in the woodland for
OL,9,Fseveral days.
OL,11,FThe prosecution, outlining their case
OL,12,Fto the jury, told them that 1,900
OL,13,Fburnt bone fragments of Claudio
OL,14,FAquilino were found trapped in the
OL,15,Froots of plants in a stream next to
OL,16,Fthe cabin where Desborough lived in
OL,17,FParamour Woods.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
