PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782400703
OL,3,CDismembered remains of two men found
OL,4,Cwith axe in woods, murder trial told
OL,6,FA piece of flesh was found by police
OL,7,Fsearch teams in the root of a tree
OL,8,Fnear a shallow grave where body parts
OL,9,Fof Daniel Coleman were discovered.
OL,11,FThe jury was told that until 18 April
OL,12,Flast year, Claudio Aquilino, despite
OL,13,Fhis addiction issues, made almost
OL,14,Fdaily contact with his family, even in
OL,15,FItaly. But after that day, all contact
OL,16,Fstopped.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
