PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782400703
OL,3,CDismembered remains of two men found
OL,4,Cwith axe in woods, murder trial told
OL,6,FThe jury heard that the day before his
OL,7,Fdisappearance, he had called the
OL,8,Fpolice, describing Desborough as "off
OL,9,Fhis head kamikaze". He said that
OL,10,FDesborough had gone to get an axe and
OL,11,Fa crowbar to attack a hotel and wanted
OL,12,Fhim to be involved, but that he didn't
OL,13,Fwant to and that was frightened of
OL,14,FDesborough.
OL,16,FThe court was told that Claudio was
OL,17,Fasked to leave the hotel on 18 April
OL,18,F2025 as that he was accused of
OL,19,Fstealing another residents' phone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
