PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782400703
OL,3,CDismembered remains of two men found
OL,4,Cwith axe in woods, murder trial told
OL,6,FCCTV shows him in a pub with
OL,7,FDesborough that day, but he was never
OL,8,Fseen again.
OL,10,FThe prosecution, Ahmed Hossain KC,
OL,11,Fsaid his bank account was accessed. He
OL,12,Ftold the jury that financial
OL,13,Finvestigators said the use of the
OL,14,Faccount was not the same as it had
OL,15,Fbeen before and described how CCTV
OL,16,Ffootage had captured Desborough using
OL,17,Fthe account.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782400703
OL,3,CDismembered remains of two men found
OL,4,Cwith axe in woods, murder trial told
OL,6,FThe jury was told that in June last
OL,7,Fyear, Desborough was seen on CCTV
OL,8,Ftravelling to London. The prosecution
OL,9,Fsay that Claudio's bank card was used
OL,10,Fto buy a train ticket and that they
OL,11,Fbelieve Desborough made the trip
OL,12,F"using a dead man's bank card as a
OL,13,Fdeliberate attempt to try to make a
OL,14,Ftrail suggesting Claudio Aquilno was
OL,15,Fstill alive and had left Cornwall".
OL,17,FMr Hossain said: "Both of these men,
OL,18,FDaniel Coleman and Claudio Aquilino,
OL,19,Fhad lived with Mr Desborough at a
OL,20,Fplace called Sandy Lodge, which was a
OL,21,Fmulti-occupancy residence in Newquay.
OL,26,@yD@ROU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
