PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782400703
OL,3,CDismembered remains of two men found
OL,4,Cwith axe in woods, murder trial told
OL,6,F"That place housed people who were
OL,7,Foften homeless or suffered with
OL,8,Faddiction issues and these two men
OL,9,Fwere last seen alive in the company of
OL,10,FJames Desborough.
OL,12,F"After each of them disappeared, their
OL,13,Fbank accounts were accessed and their
OL,14,Fmoney was spent by James Desborough.
OL,16,F"He killed them, he dismembered their
OL,17,Fbodies, he attempted to burn and bury
OL,18,Ftheir remains to conceal what he had
OL,19,Fdone, and then used their money whilst
OL,20,Fat the same time lying to those around
OL,21,Fhim about where they had gone."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU}D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
