PN,40409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782400703
OL,3,CDismembered remains of two men found
OL,4,Cwith axe in woods, murder trial told
OL,6,FThe jury was told the police began
OL,7,Fsearching the woods near Desborough's
OL,8,Fhome looking for Daniel Coleman in
OL,9,FJuly 2025.
OL,11,FIn a tree near a shallow grave where
OL,12,Fthey found remains of Mr Coleman, they
OL,13,Ffound an axe which had traces of
OL,14,FDesborough and Claudio's DNA on it.
OL,16,FIn Desborough's cabin they found the
OL,17,Fbank cards and sim card belonging to
OL,18,FClaudio Aquilno.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
