PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1782400703
OL,3,CDismembered remains of two men found
OL,4,Cwith axe in woods, murder trial told
OL,6,FThe defendant, of Old Oak Woods, Lower
OL,7,FSticker, who sat in the dock wearing a
OL,8,Fgrey T-shirt with a beard and glasses,
OL,9,Fdenies the charges and the trial
OL,10,Fcontinues.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
